{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/Logo_Evergreen_Texto.png?t=1729061889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Evergreen is a simulation game about leaving the stress of the city behind and starting a new life in a mountain valley.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This simulation game is meant to be a relaxing and calming experience. Build your house with your own hands, collect the resources that nature provides, travel to a small village to sell what you don't need, buy supplies in stores and admire the wonders of nature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/Separador.png?t=1729061889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/T\u00edtulo_Construcci\u00f3n_Casa.png?t=1729061889\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/Gif_Construcciones.gif?t=1729061889\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deep yet intuitive building system. Build your fully customized cabin so you can live comfortably in the mountains.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose the shape, size and materials of what will be your home from now on.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy furniture and appliances in a nearby village and decorate every corner to your liking.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/T\u00edtulo_Caza.png?t=1729061889\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/Gif_Ciervo.gif?t=1729061889\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hunt animals, cut down trees and search for the resources that the mountain can provide. Use those resources to build your own shelter and raise money by selling wood, animal skins or other materials.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/T\u00edtulo_ViajarPueblo.png?t=1729061889\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/Gif_Coche.gif?t=1729061889\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travel to a small town nearby with your car.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sell the raw materials you have collected to local artisans. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Visit stores and buy everything you need to make your life in the wilderness more comfortable. Furniture for your cabin, food for the winter, hunting weapons, household appliances, gasoline and much more.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/T\u00edtulo_Entorno.png?t=1729061889\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/Gif_Nieve.gif?t=1729061889\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Next-generation graphics powered by Unreal Engine 5.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a dynamic world with a day-night cycle and changing seasons. Immerse yourself in a realistic and beautiful mountain valley that will allow you to escape from the noise of the city and live a quiet and simpler life.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/extras/Separador.png?t=1729061889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow the game and add it to your Wishlist, so you don't miss any updates!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"GROWER I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997250/ffa6f035568fb45f0d5391a0d41224059484d660.jpg"},{"name":"GROWER II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997250/02eded2bb6bd5fce5a7b421b2000893593d75b03.jpg"},{"name":"GROWER III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997250/0facfa3a42dd0d084649149a207107afd5e1a115.jpg"},{"name":"HUNTER I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997250/00500b9529b6ac5223570aa8eb0ae77816eb1536.jpg"},{"name":"HUNTER II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997250/f591500dcd94f4cda0d5de29e64378129b1fa086.jpg"},{"name":"HUNTER III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997250/85e4afe39a302c1a58a68b3eb64c73036fdbda53.jpg"},{"name":"SHOPAHOLIC I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997250/a9eabfedbf5c0280c2997a72e4baba9c7b761646.jpg"},{"name":"SHOPAHOLIC II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997250/24b5cfd2bf2b89b5210a46fec2e0f8556c09ea07.jpg"},{"name":"SHOPAHOLIC III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997250/d84ad1ea395bf7a83b4f3b17528d869f3fd315a5.jpg"},{"name":"GAMER I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997250/16023064e2af4bcbd6eed036b86d737f140cb3a7.jpg"}],"total":42},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729061889","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997250/page